OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Fedging eastwards this evening, perhaps
OL,7,Fgiving the odd heavier burst, but
OL,8,Fremaining dry in some eastern areas.
OL,9,FOften dry through the early hours with
OL,10,Fthe odd spot of rain in places.
OL,11,FTurning breezier and staying very mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FOften cloudy with a little
OL,14,Fdrizzle in places, though many places
OL,15,Fstaying dry. More persistent rain
OL,16,Farriving for some later in the
OL,17,Fafternoon and turning windier. Another
OL,18,Fmild day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
