OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FWindy on
OL,6,FFriday with gales possible. Otherwise
OL,7,Fsunny spells and isolated showers.
OL,8,FMainly fine on Saturday with lighter
OL,9,Fwinds but turning windier again on
OL,10,FSunday with a few showers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
